Oxygen Workers Types

This project provides type definitions for different versions of the Oxygen environment. Please make sure you use the correct entrypoint for your project. Hydrogen will automatically configure the correct version for you.

Available entrypoints (compatibility dates)

Each entrypoint is available to import under its respective date, e.g. @shopify/oxygen-workers-types/2022-10-31.

  • 2022-10-31 (default)
  • 2023-07-01
